    "body": "Fixes a bug in generic top-k softmax EVT implementation that resulted in wrong results when k != 2 and k != 4.\r\n\r\nThis allows removal of the static assert requiring k to be either 2 or 4. Comment in example 61 is also fixed to reflect that any k value is now supported.",
